Make certifcate before running:
openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem -days XXX
XXX : the days. 1 - 999


Execute:
make
./server <certificate> <key> <port number>
./client <hostname> <port number>
make clean